\c 2
\s UElija wenyukela ezulwini
\p
\v 1 Kwasekusithi iN\nd kosi\nd* isizamenyusela uElija emazulwini ngesivunguzane\x + 1.11. Gen. 5.24.\x*, uElija wahamba loElisha\x + 1 Kho. 19.21.\x* bevela eGiligali\x + 4.38. Josh. 5.9.\x*.
\v 2 UElija wasesithi kuElisha: Akuhlale lapha\x + 1.4,6. Ruthe 1.15,16.\x*, ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* ingithumile eBhetheli\x + Josh. 16.2.\x*. Kodwa uElisha wathi: Kuphila kukaJehova lokuphila komphefumulo wakho, kangiyikukutshiya\x + 1.4,6. 1 Sam. 20.3.\x*. Basebesehlela eBhetheli.
\v 3 Lamadodana abaprofethi ayeseBhetheli aphuma eza kuElisha\x + 2.5,7,15. 4.1,38. 5.22. 6.1. 9.1. 9.4. 1 Sam. 10.10. 19.20. 1 Kho. 18.4.20.35.\x*, athi kuye: Uyazi yini ukuthi iN\nd kosi\nd* izayisusa inkosi yakho lamuhla ekhanda lakho\x + 4.38.\x*? Wasesithi: Yebo, mina ngiyazi; thulani.
\v 4 UElija wasesithi kuye: Elisha, akuhlale lapha, ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* ingithumile eJeriko\x + 1 Kho. 16.34.\x*. Kodwa wathi: Kuphila kukaJehova lokuphila komphefumulo wakho, kangiyikukutshiya\x + 2.4,6. 1 Sam. 20.3.\x*. Basebefika eJeriko.
\v 5 Amadodana abaprofethi aseJeriko asesondela kuElisha, athi kuye: Uyazi yini ukuthi lamuhla iN\nd kosi\nd* izasusa inkosi yakho ekhanda lakho\x + 4.38.\x*? Wasesithi: Yebo, mina ngiyazi; thulani.
\v 6 UElija wasesithi kuye: Akuhlale lapha, ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* ingithumile eJordani. Kodwa wathi: Kuphila kukaJehova lokuphila komphefumulo wakho, kangiyikukutshiya\x + 2.4,6. 1 Sam. 20.3.\x*. Basebehamba bobabili.
\v 7 Amadoda angamatshumi amahlanu awamadodana abaprofethi asesiyakuma khatshana maqondana \add labo\add*; \add bona\add* bobabili basebesima eJordani.
\v 8 UElija wasethatha isembatho sakhe, wa\add si\add*goqa, watshaya amanzi\x + 1 Kho. 19.19.\x*, asedabuka ngapha langapha; bobabili basebechapha emhlabathini owomileyo\x + 2.14. Eks. 14.21.\x*.
\p
\v 9 Kwasekusithi sebechaphile uElija wathi kuElisha: Cela engizakwenzela khona ngingakasuswa kuwe. UElisha wathi: Ake kuthi isabelo esiphindwe kabili somoya wakho sibe phezu kwami\x + Dute. 21.17.\x*.
\v 10 Wasesithi: Ucele ulutho olulukhuni; uba ungibona lapha ngisuswa kuwe, kuzakuba njalo kuwe; kodwa uba kungenjalo, kakuyikuba \add njalo\add*.
\v 11 Kwasekusithi besahamba, behamba bekhuluma, khangela-ke, kwaba lenqola yomlilo lamabhiza omlilo\x + 6.17. Hlab. 68.17. 104.4.\x*, kwabehlukanisa bobabili\f + \fk kwabehlukanisa: \fl Heb. \fq kwenza ukwehlukana phakathi kwabo.\f*. UElija wasesenyukela emazulwini ngesivunguzane.
\p
\v 12 UElisha wasekubona wamemeza \add wathi\add*: Baba wami! Baba wami! Inqola yakoIsrayeli labamabhiza ayo\x + 13.14.\x*! Njalo kazabe esambona. Wasebamba izigqoko zakhe, wazidabula zaba yiziqa ezimbili\x + 1 Kho. 11.30.\x*.
\v 13 Wasedobha isembatho sikaElija esawa kuye, wabuyela, wema ekhunjini lweJordani.
\v 14 Wasethatha isembatho sikaElija esawa kuye, watshaya amanzi esithi: Ingaphi iN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu kaElija? Yena-ke esewatshayile amanzi, ehlukana ngapha langapha; uElisha wasechapha\x + 2.8.\x*.
\v 15 Kwathi amadodana abaprofethi ayeseJeriko maqondana \add laye\add* embona athi: Umoya kaElija uhlezi phezu kukaElisha. Asesiza ukumhlangabeza, akhothamela emhlabathini phambi kwakhe\x + 2.7.\x*.
\s UElisha ungumprofethi
\p
\v 16 Asesithi kuye: Khangela khathesi, kulamadoda aqinileyo angamatshumi amahlanu kanye lenceku zakho; akuwayekele ahambe adinge inkosi yakho; mhlawumbe uMoya weN\nd kosi\nd* uyenyusile wayiphosela kwenye yezintaba, loba kwesinye sezihotsha. Wasesithi: Lingathumi\x + 1 Kho. 18.12.\x*.
\v 17 Sebemphikelele waze waba lenhloni, wathi: Thumani. Basebethuma amadoda angamatshumi amahlanu; adinga insuku ezintathu, kodwa awamtholanga\x + 8.11. Hlu. 3.25.\x*.
\v 18 Asebuyela kuye ehlezi eJeriko, wathi kuwo: Kangitshongo yini kini \add ukuthi\add*: Lingahambi?
\p
\v 19 Amadoda omuzi asesithi kuElisha: Ake ukhangele, indawo yalumuzi inhle njengoba inkosi yami ibona; kodwa amanzi mabi, lomhlabathi kawuvundanga.
\v 20 Wasesithi: Ngilethelani umganu omutsha, lifake itshwayi kuwo. Basebe\add wu\add*letha kuye.
\v 21 Wasephuma waya emthonjeni wamanzi, waphosela itshwayi kuwo\x + 2.8,14. 4.29,41. 5.10. 6.6. Eks. 15.25. Mark. 7.33. 8.23. Joha. 9.6. Eks. 7.19.\x*, wathi: Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*: Ngiwelaphile amanzi la; kakusayikuba khona ukufa lokungatheli okuvela lapho\x + 2.19.\x*.
\v 22 Amanzi aseselatshwa kuze kube lamuhla, njengelizwi likaElisha alikhulumayo.
\p
\v 23 Wasesenyuka esuka lapho waya eBhetheli; kwathi esenyuka endleleni kwaphuma\x + 1 Kho. 3.7. Gen. 44.20. 1 Sam. 20.35.\x* abantwanyana emzini, bamklolodela bathi kuye: Yenyuka, mpabanga ndini! Yenyuka, mpabanga ndini!
\v 24 Wasenyemukula, wababona wabaqalekisa ngebizo leN\nd kosi\nd*. Kwaphuma amabhere amabili amasikazi ehlathini, adabula abafana abangamatshumi amane lambili kubo.
\v 25 Wasesuka lapho, waya entabeni iKharmeli, esuka lapho wabuyela eSamariya.